{
  "id": "2652459605_4",
  "title": "要拍女性觉醒，先安排女主当妾？",
  "content": "<div class=\"rich_media_content js_underline_content autoTypeSetting24psection\" id=\"js_content\">\n <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span data-mpa-action-id=\"mcljiv2i13b4\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n    <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 165, 235);font-weight: bold;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     滚筒洗衣机\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   近日，笔者发现，正在播出的《桃花映江山》《锦绣芳华》《橘祥如意》等多部以女性视角展开的国产剧里，女主竟都是以当男主的妾室为切入点展开叙事的——\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   杨紫、李现主演的《锦绣芳华》，承接上一部《国色芳华》，女主何惟芳（杨紫 饰）因着与县主李幼贞（张雅钦饰）的矛盾陷入危局，男主蒋长扬（李现 饰）为了救她，谎称她是自己即将娶进门的妾室，才逃过宁王的追问。这一部讲述的，正是二人婚后的故事。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;'>\n  <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"504975911\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/yl6JkZAE3SicLFic2cPia2LEKzThQzyJy95hVTxVj2oPeuVHrh9nZywlypbYn2U3IP5GpibE5K4BEzz8f4wIMvEDew/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;padding: 0px;display: block;margin-top: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: MicrosoftYaHei;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.5px;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 1080px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(248, 249, 249);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;height: auto !important;\"/>\n </section>\n <p data-mpa-action-id=\"mcljk7xei1h\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" mpa-font-style=\"mcljk7wxai0\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 14px;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" textstyle=\"\">\n    《锦绣芳华》剧照\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   刘学义、孟子义主演的《桃花映江山》中，当朝左相沈在野（刘学义 饰）因他人计谋被迫迎娶和亲公主姜桃花（孟子义 饰）为妾，桃花一进相府，就被男主的正妻、妾室轮番“考验”，四个女人都能打一桌麻将了。后面男女主更是结了又离，离了又结……\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;'>\n  <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"504975909\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/yl6JkZAE3SicLFic2cPia2LEKzThQzyJy958uUkAkhz8z5W4vHfXgKGIYEdgOWjRUL531PnDuH7bdOVs9VWOQF0Xg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;padding: 0px;display: block;margin-top: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: MicrosoftYaHei;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.5px;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 1080px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(248, 249, 249);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;width: 1080px;height: auto !important;\"/>\n </section>\n <p data-mpa-action-id=\"mcljj2r01j5r\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" mpa-font-style=\"mcljj2qifxq\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 14px;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" textstyle=\"\">\n    《桃花映江山》剧照\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   黄维德、王瑞昌、关畅、陈紫函主演的《橘祥如意》，改编自琦君经典小说《橘子红了》，讲的则是经营橘子产业的沈家老爷沈晏清（黄维德 饰）与六弟沈晏洲（王瑞昌 饰），同时爱上家境困顿却奋发向上的秀橘（关畅 饰），但大太太庄惠（陈紫函 饰）为了延续香火，设计安排秀橘嫁给了沈晏清为妾。四角恋的发展，剪不断理还乱。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section data-mpa-action-id=\"mcljj9kpoem\" nodeleaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;'>\n  <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"504975907\" data-ratio=\"0.6669921875\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/yl6JkZAE3SicLFic2cPia2LEKzThQzyJy95RQrxGibTozjN8TgiaVnbTay7Kgs7icdpglDR5J2Fv1h6ES86pbVpp5ykA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;padding: 0px;display: block;margin-top: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: MicrosoftYaHei;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.5px;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 1080px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(248, 249, 249);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;width: 1080px;height: auto !important;\"/>\n </section>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span data-mpa-action-id=\"mcljj9kp1xmb\" leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" textstyle=\"\">\n    《橘祥如意》剧照\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   虽然多线发展的感情故事里，狗血情节能让观众看得津津有味，但这些一上来就给人做妾的人设，着实令笔者膈应，忍不住要问——\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   要拍女性觉醒，就一定要先演个妾室吗？\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   “Girls help girls”，就一定要在n个女生抢一个男主的雌竞下书写吗？\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   挣脱封建礼制的枷锁，就一定要先把金丝雀锁在牢笼里吗？\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   以《橘祥如意》为例，老爷沈晏清一开始爱上秀橘，正因为她与大太太是截然不同的两种女性，她对自由独立的向往，坚韧自强的个性，在老爷眼中宛如青橘一样，心向往之。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   尽管它从许多台词和表现形式上，看上去比李少红版《橘子红了》思想要“进步”许多，但从本质来说，并没有脱离我爱空中自由飞翔的小鸟，却仍要用爱的名义想要把她锁在笼中让其折翼的架构。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;'>\n  <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"504975908\" data-ratio=\"0.6669921875\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/yl6JkZAE3SicLFic2cPia2LEKzThQzyJy95j1w6Zyb5oSM1uahGmVGjZ9qHVrt1LklWkYdPfzyPfRXTBFYVgJDjtQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;padding: 0px;display: block;margin-top: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: MicrosoftYaHei;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.5px;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 1080px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(248, 249, 249);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;width: 1080px;height: auto !important;\"/>\n </section>\n <p data-mpa-action-id=\"mcljjhea1weq\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" mpa-font-style=\"mcljjhdu1ir1\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 14px;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" textstyle=\"\">\n    究竟是爱意，还是喜欢那种调教和控制的感觉？\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   就像电影《芭比》一语中的，世界看起来更平等了，但实际上，只是父权藏得更好了。用更高明的方式，麻痹更多觉醒女性的心智，从而更好的服务于男性所主导的世界罢了。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   恰恰因为这种技巧上的进步和隐晦，女性想要真正摆脱世俗的束缚，才难上加难，因为它一上来就先把女性放在一个默认比男性低一等的设定下，女性角色只能时时刻刻都在温水煮青蛙的境遇里徘徊。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   正如《锦绣芳华》里女主何惟芳所言，“我们女子本来就不易，何必耍什么手段，彼此相残呢？我这里有很多才艺超群的女子，她们早已冲出了内宅，都过得怡然自乐。”“怎能因为被禽兽抓了一把，就要赔上自己的一生呢？”\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;'>\n  <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"504975910\" data-ratio=\"1.376953125\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/yl6JkZAE3SicLFic2cPia2LEKzThQzyJy95t2RrEz8w7aibQcqbDGxuJPYRnKTclwr7ocDOpVbJWwvk49R4o2UicpZg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;padding: 0px;display: block;margin-top: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: MicrosoftYaHei;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.5px;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 1080px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(248, 249, 249);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;width: 1080px;height: auto !important;\"/>\n </section>\n <p data-mpa-action-id=\"mcljjruq14e1\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" mpa-font-style=\"mcljjru9nd3\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 14px;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" textstyle=\"\">\n    《锦绣芳华》台词\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   这种点醒女性的台词，在当下许多大女主的剧集中层出不穷。但真正能将这一理念贯彻始终的电视剧，却寥寥无几。大部分看似女性觉醒的剧集，最后仍流于依靠一个上位者视角的男主屈尊降贵地无条件付出。比如《梦华录》的后半段，看似女性觉醒，实则沦为男主娇妻。即便主打“双强”设定，《淮水竹亭》仍一直用“淮竹虽为妾，但霸业从未娶妻”，作为男主深情人设的注解，亦是同理。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   须知真正的平等，不是靠这种强行设定的高位者的施舍达成的，里边的分寸感，差之毫厘，谬以千里。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   这种唤人觉醒，必先令人身陷囹圄的设定，又何尝不是一种套路？讨巧的角色，真的是女主吗？难道不是在背后默默支持她的男主更苏？剧本的底层逻辑和高光设定，实际上是非常微妙的反转。这也是为什么许多大女主剧中，最后爆的角色反而是男主，因为女主往往沦为了赋魅男主的摄像机镜头。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   最后，借用《书卷一梦》里面女主宋一梦（李一桐 饰）call back《新闻女王》的台词收尾：“你们知不知道，在TVB里，‘找个男人嫁了吧’这句话，是骂人的啊？”\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;'>\n  <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"504975912\" data-ratio=\"1.248046875\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/yl6JkZAE3SicLFic2cPia2LEKzThQzyJy95KwNKVzSdEHmB8sdv30vTOJNYXRR8S4ojPUx8xSYxNbX6V8KewMadJA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;padding: 0px;display: block;margin-top: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb